  <brief_title>Phase II Study in Patients With Operable Breast Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Study of Pre-Operative Pegylated Liposomal Doxorubicin (PLD), Paclitaxel, and Trastuzumab in Patients With Operable Breast Cancer Over-expressing Her2-neu</official_title>
