  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will evaluate the safety and efficacy of the combination PLD, paclitaxel, and
      trastuzumab in patients with operable breast cancer. Patients will be treated with the
      combination for 18 weeks, followed by surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
